           alt="Ladies Let's Talk matching dashboard"
           loading="lazy"
           style="max-width:320px; height:auto;">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="h5">Role &amp; Responsibilities</h2>
          <ul class="mb-0">
            <li>Served as project lead for learner management and matching automation.</li>
            <li>Designed relational tables for learners, volunteers, and matches to replace fragmented spreadsheets.</li>
            <li>Implemented scripts to generate match scores based on availability, location, and partner preferences.</li>
            <li>Documented workflows and created training materials for non-technical program staff.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="h5">Technical Highlights</h2>
          <ul class="mb-0">
            <li>Normalized intake form data into a consistent schema with validation and type-checking.</li>
            <li>Built a matching algorithm that prioritizes preferred partners, time-zone alignment, and recurring time slots.</li>
            <li>Added archival scripts to preserve historical cohorts while keeping active data sets lean.</li>
            <li>Exposed key metrics (fill rate, unmatched learners, volunteer utilization) via simple dashboards.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h2 class="h5">Impact</h2>
      <p class="card-text mb-2">
        The system cut the time required to build each cohort&apos;s matches from days to hours, and reduced
        errors caused by manual copy-paste operations. Program coordinators now have a repeatable process to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Import new learner and volunteer data.</li>
        <li>Run the matching algorithm with clear criteria.</li>
        <li>Export final match lists and send introduction emails.</li>
        <li>Track historical cohorts and re-engage volunteers over time.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

